author: Jason Brennan
title: Life | Watch: Irish people taste American Halloween treats
text:
Irish people doing things they're not used to.
Or else Irish people doing things they're pretending they've never done before, and putting their reactions on camera, for the purpose of a nicely cut together video for your visual consumption.
Call it what you want, we like them, and thanks to Facts YouTube channel, we're seeing a lot more of it.
They've just brought out a Halloween themed episode which sees them tasting American Halloween treats, which look pretty awful. Enjoy.
